data.title: Other Orchid Resources in Germany
data.meta_description: Results for other orchid resources in Germany. A worldwide directory, OrchidWire has been connecting orchid enthusiasts since 1996.
data.text:
albiflora.eu

A site dedicated to the science and aesthetics of white-flowered variations of European orchids. Peter Zschunke. Frankfurt, Hesse, Germany.

Bumblebee's Orchids

Videos on orchid culture, nursery tours, and other topics of interest to enthusiasts. Germany.

Eerika's Bilder

More than 4700 images of orchid species and hybrids. Springe, Lower Saxony, Germany.

Erdorchideen

Information focused on terrestrial orchids including their nutrient requirements and propagation. Frank Meissner. Lengenbostel, Lower Saxony, Germany.

G체nther's Homepage

European orchid information including images, pollination, travel reports, and natural hybrids. Gunther Blaich. Weinheim, Baden-W체rttemberg, Germany.

Lonis Orchideenforum

German language forum with sections on many orchid-related topics. Munich, Bavaria, Germany.

miramis.de

Exploring Europe to search for orchids is documented in images and words. Peter Zschunke. Frankfurt, Hesse, Germany.

myorchi.de

Various aspects of orchid culture are discussed in videos by a professional grower. Germany.

Orchideen Bilder

Orchid information with images of a sunroom construction using a large crane. Lower Saxony, Germany.

Orchideen im Garten

Information focusing on frost-resistant terrestrial orchids, especially Cypripediums. Wolfgang Leverberg. Remscheid, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany.

Orchideen Pflegen

Orchid buying and care tips. Andreas Bernhard. Walleshausen, Bavaria, Germany.

Orchideen Ratgeber

General orchid information and care guide. Germany.

Orchideen-Forum

A community of orchid enthusiasts, from beginners to experts, who discuss many orchid topics in the German language. Berlin, Germany.

Orchideen-Hobby-Wining

Images and live film presentations involving orchid travel to other countries. D채nischenhagen, Schleswig-Holstein, Germany.

Orchideen-Tinchen

Information about several genera of orchids. Martina Lippold. Dreieich, Hesse, Germany.

Orchideen.eu

A collection of orchid care topics is presented. Wiesmoor, Lower Saxony, Germany.

Orchideenfans Blog

Orchid news, growing tips, events, and more. Hamburg, Germany.

Orchideenfieber.de

Information about orchid care, propagation, and history. Heidelberg, Baden-W체rttemberg, Germany.

Orchideenforum.de

Informative articles with lots of culture tips, images, resource links, and more. Ingrid Pape. Rosdorf, Lower Saxony, Germany.

Orchideeninformationen

Orchid information primarily on European terrestrial orchids. Labor Walter Bongers. Gladbeck, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany.

orchideenkultur.net

Providing a platform for the exchange of all types of orchid information. Berthold Gross. Marl, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany.

Parishianae Sektion

Information about some of the smaller Phalaenopsis species and hybrids. Wolfgang Apel. Offenbach, Hesse, Germany.
